    <li>You're not sure which business structure fits your plan</li>
    <li>Your industry may have foreign ownership restrictions</li>
    <li>You need help preparing IRC/ERC documents</li>
    <li>You want to understand tax obligations before committing</li>
    <li>You've hit a roadblock with registration and don't know why</li>
  </ul>

